OL,3,C'Ketamine Queen' gets 15 years for
OL,4,Cselling Matthew Perry drugs
OL,6,FThe woman who sold ketamine to Friends
OL,7,Fstar Matthew Perry before his death
OL,8,Fwas sentenced to 15 years in prison on
OL,9,FWednesday.
OL,11,FDubbed the 'Ketamine Queen', 42-year-
OL,12,Fold Jasveen Sangha pled guilty to five
OL,13,Fcharges last September, including
OL,14,Fproviding the ketamine that led to
OL,15,FPerry's death in 2023.
OL,17,FThe American-British dual-national
OL,18,Fbecame the third defendant sentenced
OL,19,Fof the five people who have pleaded
OL,20,Fguilty in connection with the overdose
OL,21,Fof the 54-year-old actor.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
