OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775754356
OL,3,C'Ketamine Queen' gets 15 years for
OL,4,Cselling Matthew Perry drugs
OL,6,FKeith Morrison, Perry's stepfather
OL,7,Ftold the judge that he and Perry's
OL,8,Fmother, Suzanne, feel a "daily,
OL,9,Fgrinding sadness and sorrow".
OL,11,FProsecutors said the 'Ketamine Queen'
OL,12,Fhad an elaborate drug operation
OL,13,Fcatering to high-end clients to fund
OL,14,Fher jet-setting lifestyle, despite a
OL,15,Flife of privilege.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
