PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775754356
OL,3,C'Ketamine Queen' gets 15 years for
OL,4,Cselling Matthew Perry drugs
OL,6,FPerry had been using the drug through
OL,7,Fhis regular doctor as a legal off-
OL,8,Flabel treatment for depression, but
OL,9,Fsought more.
OL,11,FDr. Salvador Plasencia, admitted to
OL,12,Fillegally selling Perry ketamine and
OL,13,Fwas sentenced to 2 1/2 years in prison.
OL,15,FFollowing this, Sangha sold Perry 25
OL,16,Fvials of ketamine, including the fatal
OL,17,Fdose, for $6,000 in cash four days
OL,18,Fbefore his death, prosecutors said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
