PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775754356
OL,3,C'Ketamine Queen' gets 15 years for
OL,4,Cselling Matthew Perry drugs
OL,6,FAnother doctor, who admitted to
OL,7,Fproviding Plasencia the ketamine he
OL,8,Fsold to Perry, was sentenced to eight
OL,9,Fmonths of home detention.
OL,11,FPerry's assistant and his friend, who
OL,12,Fadmitted acting as the actor's
OL,13,Fmiddlemen, are awaiting sentencing.
OL,15,FThe judge said she is calibrating how
OL,16,Fto sentence each of the five
OL,17,Fdefendants to make sense as a whole.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
