PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775754356
OL,3,C'Ketamine Queen' gets 15 years for
OL,4,Cselling Matthew Perry drugs
OL,6,FSangha is the only defendant whose
OL,7,Fplea deal included an acknowledgment
OL,8,Fof causing Perry's death, meaning her
OL,9,F15-year prison term is likely to be
OL,10,Flonger than all the other defendants
OL,11,Fcombined.
OL,13,FSangha pleaded guilty in September to
OL,14,Fone count of using her home for drug
OL,15,Fdistribution, three counts of
OL,16,Fdistribution of ketamine, and one
OL,17,Fcount of distribution of ketamine
OL,18,Fresulting in death.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
