PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775754356
OL,3,C'Ketamine Queen' gets 15 years for
OL,4,Cselling Matthew Perry drugs
OL,6,FShe also admitted to selling drugs to
OL,7,Fanother man, 33-year-old Cody McLaury,
OL,8,Fwho had no connection to Perry, before
OL,9,Fhis overdose death in 2019.
OL,11,FThe prosecution said that despite
OL,12,FSangha's plea, she continued drug
OL,13,Fdealing, showing her lack of remorse.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
